fulltitle: Church Committee: Covert Action in Chile, 1963-73 (BC.2)
title: Church Committee: Covert Action in Chile, 1963-73 (BC.2)
description:
'Our Hidden History' Audiobooks: https://sellfy.com/OurHiddenHistory More Church Committee Reports: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBINnEpNu5u5DDKZr3zRDb9v_Q2pV55dA ---- This is The Church Committee's "Covert Action in Chile 1963-73" (Part Two: "The Range of Covert Action in Chile"). The official name of the Church Committee was "Senate Select Committee To Study Governmental Operations With Respect to Intelligence Activities". A copy of the report may also be found on the U.S. Senate Select Committee on Intelligence web site: http://www.intelligence.senate.gov/pdfs94th/94chile.pdf

II. The Ringe of Covert Action in Chile
    A. Covert Action and other Clandestine Activities
    B. Covert Action in Chile: Techniques
    C. Covert Action and Multinational Corporations

This audio recreation was narrated by John Hawkes (https://www.fiverr.com/johnhawkes) and produced by D. Giglio for 'Our Hidden History'

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
